storyInfo: Yato and Noir Corne escape from the unknown creature and seek medical aid at the village of Roka, where they run into the Felynes again. As they exchange information, they are interrupted by an old man.

attributes.content: 12 o'clock—no, 4 o'clock!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: 7 o'clock now! It's coming—
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Raise your shield!
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Are you okay?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: I'm fine.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Did it just... breathe fire?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Obviously.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Even the rocks are charred. Haven't seen anything like that since Blaze's arts.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: And I'm sure she'd love to have a go at it.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Watch out! Here it comes!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Ngh!
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: It's no good!
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Its movements are too large. Whenever we try to counterattack, it just pushes us away or flies out of range.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: We're stuck on the defensive. We have to try to close the distance.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Watch out, Yato—
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: I'm fine.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Think about its movements... It whips its tail left and right while on the ground before charging forward to bite...
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: It also accelerates to charge, and flies up to breathe fire!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Tailspin, bite, charge, fire breath... here comes the tail, Corne!
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Oof! Got it!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: At the very least, we have to be able to close in.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: You want to try that? The timing might be hard though.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: I was thinking the same thing... over here!
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: It's cumbersome... Phew—it needs time to find its footing after movement.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: We can take that opportunity to get in close.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Get me above its neck. I'll try to kill it in one blow.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Ready—dodge!
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Here we go!
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Noir Corne and I knew what to do. We've done this many times.
The moment I step onto the shield, I feel a great force from beneath, sending me into the sky.
My sword draws a sharp arc through the air and heads straight down, nothing between it and its target.
What?
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: My sword was deflected!
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Look out!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: It's taking off!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Ugh, that roar—
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: My head's buzzing—I can't move—
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: (It's preparing to breathe fire! Dodge to the side!)
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Argh!
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Yato!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: You're hurt! Are you okay?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: It just grazed my arm, I'm fine. I didn't expect it to dive like that all of a sudden.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Yato... you dropped your sword.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: I... I can't keep a grip on it.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: What... happened to my arm?
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Seems like something else drew its attention. It's looking away.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Let's get out of here while we can!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Coming through! Here comes the cart!
attributes.name: Strange White Creature

attributes.content: Push!
attributes.name: Strange White Creature

attributes.content: Where to?
attributes.name: Strange Yellow Creature

attributes.content: Don't ask meow! Just push!
attributes.name: Strange White Creature

attributes.content: Yato, those strange Felines are coming over with what looks like a bunch of scrap wood...
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Hey, what are you doing? Get away from Yato!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: I'm warning you! Don't even think about putting her on that thing!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Were mew trimming the Rathalos's claws, horned 'Hunter'?
attributes.name: Strange White Creature

attributes.content: Mew can't pawssibly win fur now! Hop on!
attributes.name: Strange White Creature

attributes.content: Can't pawssibly!
attributes.name: Strange Yellow Creature

attributes.content: Stay away! I'm warning you!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Don't touch me! Hey, not there... put me down!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Get on!
attributes.name: Strange White Creature

attributes.content: No—
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Smithy? Is this really how we're supposed to push? Why is the cart so rickety?
attributes.name: Strange White Creature

attributes.content: Mrow? So you've only ever seen other Felynes push their carts?
attributes.name: Strange White Creature

attributes.content: Where... where am I?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: What's this? A cart... made of wood? Feels like it could fall apart any moment.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: My head hurts... something hit me...
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Yato... Yato! Where is she?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Hey, horned Hunter! Where are your herbs?
attributes.name: Strange White Creature

attributes.content: ...Herbs? What herbs?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Then what about antidotes?
attributes.name: Strange White Creature

attributes.content: What are you talking about...?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Surely mew have Blue Mushrooms on mew? Good thing I have Antidote Herbs.
attributes.name: Strange White Creature

attributes.content: Mushrooms...? Why would I carry mushrooms with me?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: That's not good. Are New World Hunters always so un-purr-pared?
attributes.name: Strange White Creature

attributes.content: Un-purr-pared?
attributes.name: Strange Yellow Creature

attributes.content: Who are you? Local Felines?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Fel-INE? No, FEEL-yne! F-E-L-Y-N-E!
attributes.name: Strange White Creature

attributes.content: I'm a top researcher from Bherna Village, furmer Royal Purr-leontology Scrivener, a blue-blooded Felyne Scholar! I'm here to study the New World!
attributes.name: Strange White Creature

attributes.content: Mrow!
attributes.name: Strange Yellow Creature

attributes.content: And this is Smithy from Purr-okke village! We met along the way.
attributes.name: Strange White Creature

attributes.content: Artisan! Felyne Artisan!
attributes.name: Strange Yellow Creature

attributes.content: We're both Felynes!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Felyne!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: So you're Felynes... but not Felines?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Never mew mind that! The girl's been purr-oisoned by the Rathalos. She needs an antidote, now!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: W-What happened to Yato? You said she's poisoned?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: She's unconscious fur now. I did some furst-aid, but the purr-oison's still there.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Rathalos poison's really dangerous. It can even kill a Rhenopurr-los this big!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: I need to— Put me down!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: I thought New World Hunters were the elite of the elite, but this one's not so smart.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: They don't even have antidotes! What to do? The lass is pretty badly purr-oisoned, and there are no suitable mushrooms in the forest...
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Village!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: Right, the fastest way is to get some from a village! Remember the one that we saw from a distance?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: The Hunters there can't pawssibly lack basic ingredients like these! I'm so smart!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Mrow?
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: Hey, dumb horned Hunter! We're going to go get Blue Mushrooms fur the antidote!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Find a camp to rest at and wait fur us!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Camp? Where? Hey!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: No time to waste! Let's go!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Mrow!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: That night, the sky was set on fire, and the great monster came down from the forest, trying to burn the village down with its flames!
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: The village hunter stepped forward and told the others, 'I'm a hunter, so I'll protect the village!'
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: 'How dare you try to stop my flames of destruction, puny little hunter!'
attributes.name: Child Playing the Monster

attributes.content: 'You won't take another step forward, monster!'
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: The hunter raises his weapon and fights the monster threatening the village.
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: Giant fireball!
attributes.name: Child Playing the Monster

attributes.content: Hnf! Haah!
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: (Wrestles)
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: Argh!
attributes.name: Child Playing the Monster

attributes.content: Ha!
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: I win!
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: I told you! The hunter always wins!
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: No! I didn't lose!
attributes.name: Child Playing the Monster

attributes.content: Don't be a sore loser! I took you down!
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: The hunter never loses, no matter how scary the monster is!
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: No...
attributes.name: Child Playing the Monster

attributes.content: Dad told me that there aren't any hunters anymore.
attributes.name: Child Playing the Monster

attributes.content: You're lying! Old Kashiwau living on the south side of the village is a great hunter!
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: Dad says old Kashiwau is just a stubborn old man.
attributes.name: Child Playing the Monster

attributes.content: There aren't any hunters left because the village doesn't need them anymore. That's why the monster won't lose!
attributes.name: Child Playing the Monster

attributes.content: The fallen red leaves on the ground tell of late autumn.
The houses in the village are well-maintained, but feel solemn, even sorrowful, under the clouded sky.
A lonely statue gazes into the distance.
Wounded travelers may not be welcome here.
Hunters have long been unwelcome.
Wake up, Yato.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Those... Felynes... said you're poisoned. Do you remember? You need to stay awake.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Stop shaking me... I'm can hear you.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: How do you feel?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: My head feels heavy, and my arm's swollen. Must be the poison.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Their first aid treatment worked. I feel a little better.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: That flying creature's claws were venomous. It's my fault for not dodging...
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: No, it's not.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Those two creatures... they call themselves Felynes. Might be a unique local Feline variant.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: We shouldn't have let them go. They seemed to know about the creature. We should have learned everything we could from them first.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: What was it they said... they're looking for an antidote? Sorry, I'll go after them. You rest here.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: No, we need to go to the village, now.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: What? But you're injured, and they told us to wait...
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: We need to go as soon as possible. There's a huge monster in the forest. We don't know if it'll threaten the village directly, but it was clearly responsible for those marks.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: So it must have something to do with the Oripathy, and we have no way to prevent it from moving over a large area. That's what matters right now.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: I don't know if the village is already aware of the creature, but our top priority is to communicate the situation to the villagers and organize an evacuation to prevent the infection from spreading.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: But you need rest.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: The mission comes first. We need to ensure the villagers' safety.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Fine... I remember the way. I'll carry you there.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Corne.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Yeah?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: No need to carry me... I can walk on my own.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Don't mew think there's something odd about this village, Smithy?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Mrow?
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: I've traveled across the kingdom with the Scriveners.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: I've climbed the walls of Castle Schrade, watched the waves at Moga Village, seen countless meowgnificent sights...
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: But I'm pawsitive I've never seen a village like this!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Did you see those villagers? They looked like humans, but had ears and tails like ours!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: I'm sure there's no record of them in all the libraries of Dundorma.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Not to meowntion, we didn't see a single Hunter!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: There's a Rathalos in the forest, but no Hunters in the village, no gathering hub. How are they supposed to deal with the meownster?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: If this village wasn't founded by the Research Commission, then could this pawssibly not be the New World...? I don't understand. Where are we?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: So excited!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: W-What? Why?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Wait, Smithy! Do you remember the Rathalos that we ran into? The big guy that suddenly appeared in the forest and came after us?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Then there was a light! Could that have been...? Wait, Smithy?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Smithy? Where are you?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: We're at the village. Are you okay?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: I said I... *cough* I'm fine...
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: (She's running a high fever...)
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Let's stop and rest here.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: I'll find help.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Hey! Can anybody help? Someone's hurt!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Anybody? Hello?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: (Far away) Chikushou! Catch it! That yellow thing!
attributes.name: Angry Villager

attributes.content: (Far away) Hurry! It went that way!
attributes.name: Agitated Villager

attributes.content: Where is everybody?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: (Far away) There! The thief went that way!
attributes.name: Anxious Villager

attributes.content: Corne...
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: I'm getting dizzy... Did you evacuate the villagers?
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: No, this wasn't me.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Thank you... *cough*
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Stop talking. Save your strength.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Isn't it funny? We just started, but somehow this feels like the end...
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: D-D-Don't say stuff like that!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Yato... Yato! Say something!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Crap! Anyone?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Excuse me?
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: Do you guys need help?
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: Yes, yes! She's badly hurt.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Let me see... was it an animal that did this?
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: Yes!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: There's a place that can help her. I'll take you there!
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: —! Thank you!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Over here!
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: So shiny!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: Want this too!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: So many new tools and meowterials! Yay!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: Kuso! Where did that yellow thief get off to?
attributes.name: Angry Villager

attributes.content: H-He just went that way! Zipped right past my feet!
attributes.name: Timid Villager

attributes.content: After him!
attributes.name: Angry Villager

attributes.content: Smithy! Over here!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: What did mew do? Why are so many people after mew?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Look! So much new stuff!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: Meow goodness! Don't take people's stuff like that!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: He's here!
attributes.name: Angry Villager

attributes.content: Hey, there's another one?
attributes.name: Angry Villager

attributes.content: Oh whiskers— let's get to the forest!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: The thief went that way!
attributes.name: Angry Villager

attributes.content: The entrance to the forest is blocked! Hey, is that a Hunter's hut?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: A Hunter Hut!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: Stop running off like that!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Over here! There's a hole here!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Where did those Felines go?
attributes.name: Angry Villager

attributes.content: Shh—
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: That's... the Kashiwau house. The old man would never let them in.
attributes.name: Agitated Villager

attributes.content: Ano yarou-domo... Let's look over there! Don't let them get away!
attributes.name: Angry Villager

attributes.content: Are they gone? Whew!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Mrrowagh!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: What is it this time?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Mrrowagh!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: J-Just some furs hanging off the wall.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: But this place really looks just like a Hunter's House...
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Up there! Can! Mushrooms!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: Where? Let me see... on the shelves? Oh, they do indeed appurr to be Blue Mushrooms.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Let's try them. They could make a good antidote!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Shh... pawsteps! Get down!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Let's scampurr!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Mrow! The entrance's boarded up!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: What to do... Is there somewhere we can hide?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: (Swings a hammer) Meow!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: I-I suppose that's one way to do it...
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: The pawsteps are getting closer! We have to do this...
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Listen, Smithy, when they come in, jump onto the nearest purr-son's head.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Then do THIS with the hammer!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: I'll run past them while they're distracted, and you follow. Understand?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: So excited!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: On meow mark!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Three!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Two!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: One!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Mrow!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Almost there... that's the one. It's old Kashiwau's house.
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: He's the village hunter. A good man.
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: He has a lot of things in his house for treating injuries caused by beasts. He can help you.
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: Thank you so much...
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: No need to thank me. By the way, my name's Kazuya.
attributes.name: Child in Hunter Garb

attributes.content: Old Kashiwau often goes into the mountains to hunt and comes back with lots of stuff. He's amazing.
attributes.name: Kazuya

attributes.content: He also spent a lot of time building a fence around the village so the animals can't get in. He really cares for everyone.
attributes.name: Kazuya

attributes.content: Sounds like quite the guy!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Hang in there, Yato. We're almost there.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: *cough*...
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Oh, he seems to be out. Just pull that stick down to open the door.
attributes.name: Kazuya

attributes.content: But the owner's out...
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Don't worry, he likes to help people. He'd let you rest if he was here, I guarantee it.
attributes.name: Kazuya

attributes.content: Alright then.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Wait here, Yato. I'll get the door.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Is it this one? There... ouch!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Mrow!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: Ow! My head!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Smithy! Stop!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: It's... the horned Hunter?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: The F-Felines?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: With a Y! And don't you dare furget it!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Shake a couple of times... there we go.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Here, have the lass drink this.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: What is it?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: An antidote, of course... I think. There weren't any Blue Mushrooms, so I used something I found here that looked similar. I'm sure it'll work. Just drink it.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: I remember!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: You remember what?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: The newest antidote recipe... doesn't use Blue Mushrooms.
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: What? Why didn't you say— Mrow! Well, my recipe uses mushrooms. You shut up!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Will Yato get better?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: A horned weirdo who doesn't even gnaw what an antidote herb is...
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Mew wouldn't ask questions like that if mew had a brain under that horn.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: I've just never heard of anything called an antidote herb growing in Terra... Oh, Yato's fever is dropping. Thank goodness.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: So you're saying... this place is called Terra? It's not the New World?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: And you're not a Hunter like the ones we're furmiliar with...
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Oh yeah, and stop calling me horned weirdo! I'm here on a mission.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Could this pawssibly be... not the New World, but an entirely diffurent world?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: No... my plans to research the New World!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: I would have become the greatest scholar there, respurr-cted by everyone... I'm done fur!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Done fur!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: Er... maybe we should introduce ourselves.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: I'm Noir Corne. And she's...
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Yato. Mew've said it so many times now, I can't even get the name out of my fur.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: So you aren't Felines, but... Felynes? And you used to live with creatures that look very much like us, before you came here.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: In a world where Hunters and monsters exist.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Completely diffurent from here.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: So did that flying, firebreathing creature come from your world?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: The Rathalos? I couldn't say if anything similar lives here, but I am pawsitive this one came with us.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: In our world, they live with Rathians near volcanos and forests. They're really scary wyverns!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: So you were yelling at us that the creature was coming. What was the name again? Rath-something...
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Are your ears just fur show?!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: It's a Rathalos.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Rathalos... the name does sound impressive.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: It could fly so high, breathe huge fireballs, not to mention the venomous claws and a hide so tough it could stop swords... I guess it deserves a scary name.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Purr-cisely, but we have ways of handling them.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: What did you say?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: However, you're too weak, and your weapons are useless. Mew shouldn't even think about fighting a Rathalos.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: If it were the legendary Hunter from Bherna Village, he would go 'Eh!' and 'Hmph!'
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: And the Rathalos would be dead.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Just like that?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Just like that?
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: You must have Hunters capable of hunting a Rathalos in your village too, Smithy. Purr-haps you just didn't see them.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Anyway, let's set the Rathalos aside and think about how to send meow and Smithy home!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Corne...
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: I'm here. Are you feeling better?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: I've been awake for a while. I was listening to your conversation... Have the villagers been evacuated?
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: I... I haven't told them yet.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Here's what I'm thinking. We only fought the Rathalos once. We don't know what connection it has to the Originium.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: ...The chaos caused by a panic or a large-scale evacuation could make it even harder to track the true source of the Originium particles.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Not a bad point. But taking countermeasures is always the priority whenever there is risk of Oripathy infection. Never forget that.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Do you still have a fever? I have a towel here.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: I'm fine.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Oh, you're awake! Hm?
attributes.name: Kazuya

attributes.content: Oh, so you two are...
attributes.name: Kazuya

attributes.content: I-It's not like that! Shut up!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Huh? What are you talking about?
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Who are you?
attributes.name: Aged Hunter

attributes.content: Speak, or I'll have to clean bloodstains off my floor today.
attributes.name: Aged Hunter

attributes.content: Wait! Hold on!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: They got hurt in the mountains. I brought them here.
attributes.name: Kazuya

attributes.content: Hurt?
attributes.name: Aged Hunter

attributes.content: I took a scratch from a venomous claw. We used some of the ingredients here to make an antidote.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Thank you, and we apologize for bothering you. We'll be leaving now.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Ano kemono-domo...
attributes.name: Aged Hunter

attributes.content: Lie down if you're injured.
attributes.name: Aged Hunter

attributes.content: Oh...
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Yoshitaka Kashiwau.
attributes.name: Aged Hunter

attributes.content: That's my name. You can call me whatever you please.
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: I'm a hunter. There are many beasts in the forests here. Amateurs should avoid them.
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: Thank you for your assistance. We're—
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: I don't need to know who you are.
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: And you, over here.
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: Me?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: The girl's hurt. Boil some water for her.
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: And put that rag down.
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: ...Sure, right away!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Kazuya, grind this up. Dissolve it in water and apply it to the wound.
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: Right.
attributes.name: Kazuya

attributes.content: Felyne Scholar, are you trying to return to your world?
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Pawbviously.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: I don't know how you and the Rathalos got here, but do you know how to get back?
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Good question. I was looking around with Smithy, but there were nothing but trees. We can't go back the way we came, but there might be some other way in the forest.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: We can try the forest, but the odds aren't good.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: So how about making an agreement with us?
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Mrow?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: I know a place that may be able to help you return to where you came from.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Where is that?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Rhodes Island, the company Noir Corne and I work for. We often deal with... anomalous events.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Even if there's no immediate way home, it can still provide a safe refuge. Corne and I are in a similar situation ourselves.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: In return, we'll need your knowledge in case we encounter the Rathalos again.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: We... may even need to kill it, as you mentioned.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Rathalos hunt!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: Mrow... I can't make any purr-omises right now. I need some time.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: You have villages where you came from, don't you? Would you just turn a blind eye when there's a threat nearby?
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: We fought the Rathalos, a creature that has never been seen in these lands before. We know it's not something we can just leave alone.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: More importantly... it may also be linked to another crisis, one that's more familiar to Terra.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Maybe you don't understand what I'm talking about, but we have evidence that we can't afford to waste any time in dealing with the situation.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Oripathy aside... a creature of that size that breathes fire and has venomous claws is a threat simply by virtue of existing so close to a village.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: What did you say?
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: Flying... firebreathing... venomous claws? You saw the beast?
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: You've seen the Rathalos before too?
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: We encountered it in the forest, and believe it to be a non-native creature that is highly dangerous. We will continue to investigate and take appropriate measures as needed.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: It's my quarry.
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: Perfect. As an experienced local hunter who knows these forests, we could really use your skills.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: We share a common goal. We should work together. We'll ensure your safety.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Did you not hear me? I said it's my quarry.
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: I'm afraid I don't quite understand. Are you concerned about our combat abilities?
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Rhodes Island operators are well-trained and experienced in responding to emergencies. Dealing with anomalous creatures is part of our job.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: We were caught by surprise this time, but next time we'll be fully prepared.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Aho! It's my quarry, and I will hunt it... alone.
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: How dare you disrespect my claim!
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: This Rathalos is an unknown creature that we can't underestimate. It doesn't belong to you.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Ha! Look at the state you got yourself into. And you speak of combat ability?
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: Weak, worthless worms... Lower than an Originium Slug...
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: What are you thinking? No, don't dare even—
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: No offense, but you have no right to stop us from investigating the Rathalos. It's our job.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: I'm warning you, don't let me see your face in the forest! I don't care who you are!
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: Just stay away from my quarry!
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: If you interfere with our mission, we will be forced to consider you a threat and respond accordingly.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: I can only hope it doesn't come to that.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Damare!
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: ...Get out!
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: Out of my house! Now!
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: Out!
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: I got the water! Huh? What happened?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Mr. Kashiwau, why...
attributes.name: Kazuya

attributes.content: Let's go, Corne.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Wait! Hold on!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: D-Don't throw that! You take care too... E-Excuse us!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Mrow!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Wait!
attributes.name: Kazuya

attributes.content: I'm sorry, I don't know what came over him all of a sudden.
attributes.name: Kazuya

attributes.content: He's really a very nice person. That wasn't like him at all.
attributes.name: Kazuya

attributes.content: Thank you for your help, Kazuya.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: But we're fine. Go keep the old man company.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Alright...
attributes.name: Kazuya

attributes.content: I don't understand why he was so upset. Just because we're also looking for the Rathalos?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: He lives by himself with no family, far away from the rest of the village, and everything in there looked old and ragged.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Do you remember the hunter statue in the village? I thought it'd be a respected profession here.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Don't worry about it. It won't affect our mission.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: We should learn more about this village and look for clues about the Originium contamination.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: I'm sorry... I just wanted to help them.
attributes.name: Kazuya

attributes.content: Are they gone?
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: Uh-huh...
attributes.name: Kazuya

attributes.content: The girl seemed to be getting better.
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: *sigh*...
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau
